title: Expand Collapse Demo
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Demonstrates the `state` attribute with `<<so-expand>>` and `<<so-collapse>>` buttons.  The `state` prefix is a stable, known tiddler path, so the buttons can target the outline from anywhere and open/closed positions persist across page reloads.

<$button>Expand all<<so-expand "$:/demos/history-outline">></$button> <$button>Collapse all<<so-collapse "$:/demos/history-outline">></$button>

